<L>__{exterior starting grid monza day}
<A>__{james walks out to his car. tv crews. banks of photographers. commentators talk in different languages. everyone talking about niki's comeback. niki is in his car. the mechanics are talking to him in italian... but niki hears nothing. he looks at the steering wheel, the shell of the car, the gear stick. and then we see.. his hands are shaking violently. he's utterly terrified. the light turns green. they're off! other cars (including james's), roar forward. but niki is frozen.}
